Package edu.carroll.initMusic.web.form

Class NewSongForm

java.lang.Object
edu.carroll.initMusic.web.form.NewSongForm
public class NewSongForm extends Object
This form is used when a song is going to be added to a playlist. We have to pass all the song attributes so we can make the song into an object.
